cell("markdown","# Algorithms 14: Basic Matrix Arithmetic\n\n**Learning Objectives:**\n1. Design a `Matrix` class from scratch using 2D arrays\n2. Implement matrix addition, subtraction, scalar multiplication, and transpose\n3. Implement matrix multiplication using dot products\n4. Compute matrix determinants recursively via cofactor expansion\n\n**Prerequisites:** Linear Algebra\n**Estimated time:** 120 minutes\n**Textbook:** *Justin Skycak — Intro to Algorithms & Machine Learning* Chapter 14"),
