cell("markdown","---\n## Phase 2 — Experimental Verification\n\n### Pathological Case: Deep Copy vs Shallow Copy\nIf you initialize `Matrix` by just doing `self.data = data` (shallow copy), and then the user modifies the original array `data[0][0] = 99`, the `Matrix` object *magically changes* too!\n\nVerify that your `Matrix` class is immune to this by running the test below."),
